{"tid":1640574,"cid":31,"subCid":9,"title":"Reddit有人提議整紫色香港旗/徽","createTime":"2019-10-09T04:25:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T12:19:26.000Z","uid":144172,"like":9,"dislike":44,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"e1c5801a44341aaa91812f0d838804ec945144f4","tid":1640574,"uid":144172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T04:25:46.000Z","msg":"唔知有冇人之前提過<br />\n<br />\n1.紫色本身係好少用係國旗design之上<br />\n2.紫色代表紅+藍 象徵香港係一個中華文化(紅色)同英國殖民(藍色)下中西交融之地 (ps中華文化一向以紅色用於喜慶 唔一定係關共產黨事)<br />\n3.同黃色係對比色可以一齊用<br />\n4.洋紫荊可以用返紫色代表(雖然唔知之後仲會唔會用到)<br />\n<br />\n大家點睇??"},{"pid":"ce4a2d421556513e9d26bd08e6a4e7dda024ff6f","tid":1640574,"uid":255802,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T04:29:16.000Z","msg":"紫色配黃色好樣衰架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n洋紫荊其實係不祥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n乜你咁鐘意抽氣扇咩"},{"pid":"8946a962f1b41c6ed5efe0ce1a03218a89d5c1c4","tid":1640574,"uid":143151,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T04:29:23.000Z","msg":"紫色 好Gay<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過設計靚 其實冇乜所謂"},{"pid":"00564916e08bd1f903c589f5a9098feae4c41436","tid":1640574,"uid":65643,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T04:29:39.000Z","msg":"唔整"},{"pid":"f39b45e5ae1e7d404ab882db7162036fa6147d9f","tid":1640574,"uid":123175,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T04:29:48.000Z","msg":"用市政局支旗囉"},{"pid":"eb6a23cedc8d81e855d35e0e6a51e4adb2976943","tid":1640574,"uid":289603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T04:30:33.000Z","msg":"借個位....P推唔旭...<br />\n有藍group同我地做緊同一樣野‼所以我地更加之要支持以下手足參選投佢地一票<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1640572/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1640572/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"e4741deda05db3e5bf073c0806713f656f483016","tid":1640574,"uid":279023,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T04:31:46.000Z","msg":"紫色係古代生產唔到，係高級昂貴顏料，所以歷史上小紫色"},{"pid":"cf0de45fa01337a9bf3875b7c60d34f27218fbf4","tid":1640574,"uid":70818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T04:32:21.000Z","msg":"有得諗"},{"pid":"9dd565b0d902fe0a261c8b60d31367d208d9727a","tid":1640574,"uid":117301,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T04:33:04.000Z","msg":"紫色現金色<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n世界最貴既國旗"},{"pid":"b638e0973d6bdf8e66bdc128371e2e21f5cf6549","tid":1640574,"uid":6291,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T04:33:40.000Z","msg":"要睇下咩紫 好多都好核突"},{"pid":"022b0f9d786be8c9473b6adcde55a858a69a4d65","tid":1640574,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T04:34:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/ce/HKUrbanCouncil.svg/300px-HKUrbanCouncil.svg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2Fc%2Fce%2FHKUrbanCouncil.svg%2F300px-HKUrbanCouncil.svg.png&h=8de806b9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ac826c98e7947e0f8961ec3dd2877f66dcfcbd23","tid":1640574,"uid":249260,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"022b0f9d786be8c9473b6adcde55a858a69a4d65","tid":1640574,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T04:34:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/ce/HKUrbanCouncil.svg/300px-HKUrbanCouncil.svg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2Fc%2Fce%2FHKUrbanCouncil.svg%2F300px-HKUrbanCouncil.svg.png&h=8de806b9&